## <a name="luxemburg-passport-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="f3564-5412">Номер паспорта Луксембург</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f3564-5412">Luxemburg passport number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="f3564-5413">Этот объект типа конфиденциальной информации доступен только в типе конфиденциальной информации номера паспорта ЕС.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f3564-5413">This sensitive information type entity is only available in the EU Passport Number sensitive information type.</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="f3564-5414">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f3564-5414">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f3564-5415">Восемь цифр или букв без пробелов и разделителей</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f3564-5415">Eight digits or letters with no spaces or delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="f3564-5416">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f3564-5416">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f3564-5417">Восемь цифр или букв (без учета регистра)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f3564-5417">Eight digits or letters (not case sensitive)</span></span>
  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="f3564-5418">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f3564-5418">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f3564-5419">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f3564-5419">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="f3564-5420">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f3564-5420">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f3564-5421">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f3564-5421">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="f3564-5422">Регулярное выражение `Regex_nation_eu_passport_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f3564-5422">The regular expression  `Regex_nation_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="f3564-5423">Найдено ключевое слово FROM `Keywords_nation_eu_passport_number` .</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f3564-5423">A keyword from  `Keywords_nation_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
 <!-- EU Passport Number -->
<Entity id="21883626-6245-4f3d-9b61-5cbb43e625ee" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_nation_eu_passport_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_nation_eu_passport_number" />
        </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="f3564-5424">Keywords</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f3564-5424">Keywords</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f3564-5425">**Keywords_nation_eu_passport_number**</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f3564-5425">**Keywords_nation_eu_passport_number**</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f3564-5426">номер паспорта латышский паспорт паспорт нет пасснуммер</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f3564-5426">passport number latvian passport number passport no passnummer</span></span>

## <a name="luxemburg-tax-identification-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="f3564-5427">Идентификационный номер налога на Луксембург</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f3564-5427">Luxemburg tax identification number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="f3564-5428">Этот объект типа конфиденциальной информации доступен только в типе конфиденциальной информации по идентификационному номеру Европейского налога ЕС.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f3564-5428">This sensitive information type entity is only available in the EU Tax Identification Number sensitive information type.</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="f3564-5429">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f3564-5429">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f3564-5430">13 цифр без пробелов и разделителей</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f3564-5430">13 digits with no spaces or delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="f3564-5431">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f3564-5431">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f3564-5432">13 цифр:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f3564-5432">13 digits:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="f3564-5433">11 цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f3564-5433">11 digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="f3564-5434">две проверочные цифры.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f3564-5434">Two check digits</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="f3564-5435">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f3564-5435">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f3564-5436">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f3564-5436">Yes</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="f3564-5437">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f3564-5437">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f3564-5438">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 85 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f3564-5438">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="f3564-5439">Функция `Func_luxemburg_eu_tax_file_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f3564-5439">The function  `Func_luxemburg_eu_tax_file_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="f3564-5440">Найдено ключевое слово FROM `Keywords_luxemburg_eu_tax_file_number` .</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f3564-5440">A keyword from  `Keywords_luxemburg_eu_tax_file_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
<span data-ttu-id="f3564-5441">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f3564-5441">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="f3564-5442">Функция `Func_luxemburg_eu_tax_file_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f3564-5442">The function  `Func_luxemburg_eu_tax_file_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
    
```xml
 <!-- EU Tax File Number -->
<Entity id="e09c07d3-66e5-4783-989d-49ac62748f5f" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_luxemburg_eu_tax_file_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_luxemburg_eu_tax_file_number" />
        </Pattern>
<Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_luxemburg_eu_tax_file_number" />
        </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

## <a name="malaysia-identification-card-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="f3564-5482">Идентификационный номер карты Малайзии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f3564-5482">Malaysia identification card number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="f3564-5483">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f3564-5483">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f3564-5484">12 цифр, содержащих необязательные дефисы.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f3564-5484">12 digits containing optional hyphens</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="f3564-5485">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f3564-5485">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f3564-5486">12 цифр:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f3564-5486">12 digits:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f3564-5487">шесть цифр в формате ГГММДД (дата рождения);</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f3564-5487">Six digits in the format YYMMDD which are the date of birth</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="f3564-5488">дефис (необязательно);</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f3564-5488">A dash (optional)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="f3564-5489">код места рождения из двух букв;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f3564-5489">Two-letter place-of-birth code</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="f3564-5490">дефис (необязательно);</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f3564-5490">A dash (optional)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="f3564-5491">три случайные цифры;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f3564-5491">Three random digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="f3564-5492">код пола из одной цифры.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f3564-5492">One-digit gender code</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="f3564-5493">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f3564-5493">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f3564-5494">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f3564-5494">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="f3564-5495">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f3564-5495">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f3564-5496">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 85 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f3564-5496">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f3564-5497">регулярное выражение Regex_malaysia_id_card_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f3564-5497">The regular expression Regex_malaysia_id_card_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f3564-5498">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_malaysia_id_card_number.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f3564-5498">A keyword from Keyword_malaysia_id_card_number is found.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Malaysia ID Card Number -->
</Entity>
      <Entity id="7f0e921c-9677-435b-aba2-bb8f1013c749" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
            <IdMatch idRef="Regex_malaysia_id_card_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keyword_malaysia_id_card_number" />
        </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

## <a name="malta-drivers-license-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="f3564-5525">Номер водительского удостоверения для драйвера Мальта</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f3564-5525">Malta driver's license number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="f3564-5526">Этот объект типа конфиденциальной информации доступен только в типе конфиденциальной информации номера лицензии для драйвера ЕС.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f3564-5526">This sensitive information type entity is only available in the EU Driver's License Number sensitive information type.</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="f3564-5527">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f3564-5527">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f3564-5528">Сочетание двух символов и шести цифр в указанном шаблоне</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f3564-5528">Combination of two characters and six digits in the specified pattern</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="f3564-5529">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f3564-5529">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f3564-5530">Сочетание двух символов и шести цифр:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f3564-5530">Combination of two characters and six digits:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="f3564-5531">Два символа (цифры или буквы без учета регистра);</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f3564-5531">Two characters (digits or letters, not case-sensitive)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f3564-5532">пробел (необязательно); </span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f3564-5532">A space (optional)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f3564-5533">три цифры; </span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f3564-5533">Three digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f3564-5534">пробел (необязательно); </span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f3564-5534">A space (optional)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f3564-5535">Три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f3564-5535">Three digits</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="f3564-5536">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f3564-5536">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f3564-5537">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f3564-5537">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="f3564-5538">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f3564-5538">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f3564-5539">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f3564-5539">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="f3564-5540">Регулярное выражение `Regex_malta_eu_driver's_license_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f3564-5540">The regular expression  `Regex_malta_eu_driver's_license_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="f3564-5541">Найдено ключевое слово FROM `Keywords_malta_eu_driver's_license_number` .</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f3564-5541">A keyword from  `Keywords_malta_eu_driver's_license_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
<!-- EU Driver's License Number -->
 <Entity id="b8fe86d1-c056-453b-bfaa-9fe698699ecc" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_malta_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_malta_eu_driver's_license_number" />
        </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="f3564-5542">Keywords</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f3564-5542">Keywords</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f3564-5543">**Keywords_malta_eu_driver "s_license_number**</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f3564-5543">**Keywords_malta_eu_driver's_license_number**</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="f3564-5544">DL #</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f3564-5544">dl#</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f3564-5545">driver license</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f3564-5545">driver license</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="f3564-5547">Лицензия на драйвер</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f3564-5547">driver licence</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f3564-5548">Drivers лик.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f3564-5548">drivers lic.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="f3564-5551">driver's license</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f3564-5551">driver's license</span></span>

## <a name="malta-national-identification-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="f3564-5557">Национальный идентификационный номер Мальта</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f3564-5557">Malta national identification number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="f3564-5558">Этот объект типа конфиденциальной информации доступен только в типе конфиденциальной информации ЕС по национальному идентификационному номеру.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f3564-5558">This sensitive information type entity is only available in the EU National Identification Number sensitive information type.</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="f3564-5559">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f3564-5559">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f3564-5560">Семь цифр, за которыми следует одна буква</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f3564-5560">Seven digits followed by one letter</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="f3564-5561">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f3564-5561">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f3564-5562">Семь цифр, за которыми следует одна буква:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f3564-5562">Seven digits followed by one letter:</span></span>
  
-  <span data-ttu-id="f3564-5563">семь цифр;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f3564-5563">Seven digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="f3564-5564">Одна прописная буква (с учетом регистра)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f3564-5564">One uppercase letter (case sensitive)</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="f3564-5565">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f3564-5565">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f3564-5566">Неприменимо</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f3564-5566">Not applicable</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="f3564-5567">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f3564-5567">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f3564-5568">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f3564-5568">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="f3564-5569">Регулярное выражение `Regex_malta_eu_national_id_card` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f3564-5569">The regular expression  `Regex_malta_eu_national_id_card` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="f3564-5570">Найдено ключевое слово FROM `Keywords_malta_eu_national_id_card` .</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f3564-5570">A keyword from  `Keywords_malta_eu_national_id_card` is found.</span></span> 
    
<span data-ttu-id="f3564-5571">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 65 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, отдаленном не более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f3564-5571">A DLP policy is 65% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="f3564-5572">Регулярное выражение `Regex_malta_eu_national_id_card` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f3564-5572">The regular expression  `Regex_malta_eu_national_id_card` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
    
```xml
 <!--Malta national identification number  -->
<Entity id="419f449f-6d9d-4be1-a154-b531f7a91b41" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_malta_eu_national_id_card" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_malta_eu_national_id_card" />
        </Pattern>
<Pattern confidenceLevel="65">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_malta_eu_national_id_card" />
        </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

#### <a name="keywords_malta_eu_national_id_card"></a><span data-ttu-id="f3564-5574">Keywords_malta_eu_national_id_card</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f3564-5574">Keywords_malta_eu_national_id_card</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="f3564-5577">идентифика нумру Тал билжетт</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f3564-5577">identifika numru tal-biljett</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f3564-5578">кодиċи нумерали персонали</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f3564-5578">kodiċi numerali personali</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f3564-5579">нумру Ta ' идентификаззжони персонали</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f3564-5579">numru ta 'identifikazzjoni personali</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f3564-5580">нумру Ta ' идентификаззжони ТАТ такскса</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f3564-5580">numru ta 'identifikazzjoni tat-taxxa</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f3564-5581">нумру Ta ' идентификаззжони унику</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f3564-5581">numru ta 'identifikazzjoni uniku</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f3564-5582">нумру Ta ' идентитà унику</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f3564-5582">numru ta' identità uniku</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f3564-5583">нумруные зада сервизз таċ ċиттадин</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f3564-5583">numru tas-servizz taċ-ċittadin</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f3564-5584">нумру ТАТ — такскса</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f3564-5584">numru tat-taxxa</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f3564-5585">персональный числовой код</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f3564-5585">personal numeric code</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f3564-5586">уникальный идентификационный номер</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f3564-5586">unique identification number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f3564-5587">уникальный идентификационный номер</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f3564-5587">unique identity number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f3564-5588">уникуеидентитино #</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f3564-5588">uniqueidentityno#</span></span>


## <a name="malta-passport-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="f3564-5589">Номер паспорта для Мальта</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f3564-5589">Malta passport number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="f3564-5590">Этот объект типа конфиденциальной информации доступен только в типе конфиденциальной информации номера паспорта ЕС.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f3564-5590">This sensitive information type entity is only available in the EU Passport Number sensitive information type.</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="f3564-5591">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f3564-5591">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f3564-5592">Семь цифр без пробелов и разделителей</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f3564-5592">Seven digits without spaces or delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="f3564-5593">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f3564-5593">Pattern</span></span>

 <span data-ttu-id="f3564-5594">семь цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f3564-5594">Seven digits</span></span> 
  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="f3564-5595">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f3564-5595">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f3564-5596">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f3564-5596">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="f3564-5597">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f3564-5597">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f3564-5598">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f3564-5598">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="f3564-5599">Регулярное выражение `Regex_malta_eu_passport_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f3564-5599">The regular expression  `Regex_malta_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="f3564-5600">Найдено ключевое слово FROM `Keywords_malta_eu_passport_number` .</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f3564-5600">A keyword from  `Keywords_malta_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
 <!-- EU Passport Number -->
<Entity id="21883626-6245-4f3d-9b61-5cbb43e625ee" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_malta_eu_passport_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_malta_eu_passport_number" />
        </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="f3564-5601">Keywords</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f3564-5601">Keywords</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f3564-5602">**Keywords_malta_eu_passport_number**</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f3564-5602">**Keywords_malta_eu_passport_number**</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="f3564-5603">passport number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f3564-5603">passport number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f3564-5604">номер паспорта Мальтийский</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f3564-5604">maltese passport number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f3564-5605">паспорт нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f3564-5605">passport no</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f3564-5606">нумру Тал — пассапорт</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f3564-5606">numru tal-passaport</span></span>

## <a name="malta-tax-identification-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="f3564-5607">Идентификационный номер налога Мальта</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f3564-5607">Malta tax identification number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="f3564-5608">Этот объект типа конфиденциальной информации доступен только в типе конфиденциальной информации по идентификационному номеру Европейского налога ЕС.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f3564-5608">This sensitive information type entity is only available in the EU Tax Identification Number sensitive information type.</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="f3564-5609">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f3564-5609">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f3564-5610">Для национальных замальтийский: 7 цифр и одна буква в указанном шаблоне</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f3564-5610">For Maltese nationals: 7 digits and one letter in the specified pattern</span></span>
  
<span data-ttu-id="f3564-5611">Мальтийскийные страны и Мальтийский, не являющиеся субъектами: 9 цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f3564-5611">Non-Maltese nationals and Maltese entities: 9 digits</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="f3564-5612">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f3564-5612">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f3564-5613">Мальтийский национальные условия: 7 цифр и одна буква</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f3564-5613">Maltese nationals: 7 digits and one letter</span></span>
  
-  <span data-ttu-id="f3564-5614">семь цифр;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f3564-5614">Seven digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="f3564-5615">Одна буква (без учета регистра)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f3564-5615">One letter (not case-sensitive)</span></span>
    
<span data-ttu-id="f3564-5616">Мальтийскийные страны и Мальтийский, не являющиеся субъектами: 9 цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f3564-5616">Non-Maltese nationals and Maltese entities: 9 digits</span></span>
  
-  <span data-ttu-id="f3564-5617">девять цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f3564-5617">Nine digits</span></span> 
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="f3564-5618">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f3564-5618">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f3564-5619">Неприменимо</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f3564-5619">Not applicable</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="f3564-5620">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f3564-5620">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f3564-5621">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f3564-5621">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="f3564-5622">Функция `Func_malta_eu_tax_file_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f3564-5622">The function  `Func_malta_eu_tax_file_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="f3564-5623">Найдено ключевое слово FROM `Keywords_malta_eu_tax_file_number` .</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f3564-5623">A keyword from  `Keywords_malta_eu_tax_file_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
<span data-ttu-id="f3564-5624">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 65 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, отдаленном не более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f3564-5624">A DLP policy is 65% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="f3564-5625">Функция `Func_malta_eu_tax_file_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f3564-5625">The function  `Func_malta_eu_tax_file_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
    
```xml
 <!-- EU Tax File Number -->
<Entity id="e09c07d3-66e5-4783-989d-49ac62748f5f" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_malta_eu_tax_file_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_malta_eu_tax_file_number" />
        </Pattern>
<Pattern confidenceLevel="65">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_malta_eu_tax_file_number" />
        </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="f3564-5626">Keywords</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f3564-5626">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keywords_malta_eu_tax_file_number"></a><span data-ttu-id="f3564-5627">Keywords_malta_eu_tax_file_number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f3564-5627">Keywords_malta_eu_tax_file_number</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="f3564-5628">номер службы для себя</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f3564-5628">citizen service number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f3564-5629">ID ТАТ — такскса</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f3564-5629">id tat-taxxa</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f3564-5630">идентифика нумру Тал билжетт</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f3564-5630">identifika numru tal-biljett</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f3564-5631">кодиċи нумерали персонали</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f3564-5631">kodiċi numerali personali</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f3564-5632">нумру Ta ' идентификаззжони персонали</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f3564-5632">numru ta 'identifikazzjoni personali</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f3564-5633">нумру Ta ' идентификаззжони ТАТ такскса</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f3564-5633">numru ta 'identifikazzjoni tat-taxxa</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f3564-5634">нумру Ta ' идентификаззжони унику</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f3564-5634">numru ta 'identifikazzjoni uniku</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f3564-5635">нумру Ta ' идентитà унику</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f3564-5635">numru ta' identità uniku</span></span>

## <a name="netherlands-citizens-service-bsn-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="f3564-5658">Номер службы (BSN) для Нидерландов</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f3564-5658">Netherlands citizen's service (BSN) number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="f3564-5659">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f3564-5659">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f3564-5660">8–9 цифр, содержащих необязательные пробелы.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f3564-5660">8-9 digits containing optional spaces</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="f3564-5661">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f3564-5661">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f3564-5662">8–9 цифр:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f3564-5662">8-9 digits:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f3564-5663">три цифры; </span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f3564-5663">Three digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="f3564-5664">пробел (необязательно); </span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f3564-5664">A space (optional)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="f3564-5665">три цифры; </span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f3564-5665">Three digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="f3564-5666">пробел (необязательно); </span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f3564-5666">A space (optional)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="f3564-5667">2–3 цифры.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f3564-5667">2-3 digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="f3564-5668">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f3564-5668">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f3564-5669">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f3564-5669">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="f3564-5670">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f3564-5670">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f3564-5671">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 85 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f3564-5671">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f3564-5672">функция Func_netherlands_bsn находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f3564-5672">The function Func_netherlands_bsn finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f3564-5673">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_netherlands_bsn;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f3564-5673">A keyword from Keyword_netherlands_bsn is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f3564-5674">функция Func_eu_date2 находит дату в правильном формате.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f3564-5674">The function Func_eu_date2 finds a date in the right date format.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f3564-5675">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f3564-5675">The checksum passes.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Netherlands Citizen's Service (BSN) Number -->
<Entity id="c5f54253-ef7e-44f6-a578-440ed67e946d" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
       <IdMatch idRef="Func_netherlands_bsn" /> 
       <Match idRef="Keyword_netherlands_bsn" /> 
       <Match idRef="Func_eu_date2" /> 
  </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

- <span data-ttu-id="f3564-5696">уникальный идентификационный номер</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f3564-5696">unique identification number</span></span>

## <a name="netherlands-drivers-license-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="f3564-5699">Номер водительского удостоверения для Нидерландов</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f3564-5699">Netherlands driver's license number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="f3564-5700">Этот объект типа конфиденциальной информации доступен только в типе конфиденциальной информации номера лицензии для драйвера ЕС.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f3564-5700">This sensitive information type entity is only available in the EU Driver's License Number sensitive information type.</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="f3564-5701">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f3564-5701">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f3564-5702">10 цифр без пробелов и разделителей</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f3564-5702">10 digits without spaces and delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="f3564-5703">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f3564-5703">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f3564-5704">10 цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f3564-5704">10 digits</span></span>
  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="f3564-5705">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f3564-5705">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f3564-5706">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f3564-5706">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="f3564-5707">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f3564-5707">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f3564-5708">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f3564-5708">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="f3564-5709">Регулярное выражение `Regex_netherlands_eu_driver's_license_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f3564-5709">The regular expression  `Regex_netherlands_eu_driver's_license_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="f3564-5710">Найдено ключевое слово FROM `Keywords_netherlands_eu_driver's_license_number` .</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f3564-5710">A keyword from  `Keywords_netherlands_eu_driver's_license_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
 <!-- EU Driver's License Number -->
<Entity id="b8fe86d1-c056-453b-bfaa-9fe698699ecc" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_netherlands_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_netherlands_eu_driver's_license_number" />
        </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="f3564-5711">Keywords</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f3564-5711">Keywords</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f3564-5712">**Keywords_netherlands_eu_driver "s_license_number**</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f3564-5712">**Keywords_netherlands_eu_driver's_license_number**</span></span>

## <a name="netherlands-national-identification-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="f3564-5728">Национальный идентификационный номер Нидерландов</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f3564-5728">Netherlands national identification number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="f3564-5729">Этот объект типа конфиденциальной информации доступен только в типе конфиденциальной информации ЕС по национальному идентификационному номеру.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f3564-5729">This sensitive information type entity is only available in the EU National Identification Number sensitive information type.</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="f3564-5730">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f3564-5730">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f3564-5731">Девять цифр без пробелов и разделителей</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f3564-5731">Nine digits without spaces or delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="f3564-5732">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f3564-5732">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f3564-5733">Девять цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f3564-5733">Nine digits</span></span>
  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="f3564-5734">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f3564-5734">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f3564-5735">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f3564-5735">Yes</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="f3564-5736">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f3564-5736">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f3564-5737">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 85 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f3564-5737">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="f3564-5738">Функция `Func_netherlands_eu_national_id_card` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f3564-5738">The function  `Func_netherlands_eu_national_id_card` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="f3564-5739">Найдено ключевое слово FROM.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f3564-5739">A keyword from is found.</span></span>
    
<span data-ttu-id="f3564-5740">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f3564-5740">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="f3564-5741">Функция `Func_netherlands_eu_national_id_card` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f3564-5741">The function  `Func_netherlands_eu_national_id_card` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
    
```xml
 <!--Netherland national identification number  -->
<Entity id="419f449f-6d9d-4be1-a154-b531f7a91b41" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_netherlands_eu_national_id_card" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_netherlands_eu_national_id_card" />
        </Pattern>
<Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_netherlands_eu_national_id_card" />
        </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

## <a name="netherlands-passport-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="f3564-5765">Номер паспорта Нидерландов</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f3564-5765">Netherlands passport number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="f3564-5766">Этот объект типа конфиденциальной информации доступен только в типе конфиденциальной информации номера паспорта ЕС.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f3564-5766">This sensitive information type entity is only available in the EU Passport Number sensitive information type.</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="f3564-5767">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f3564-5767">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f3564-5768">Девять букв или цифр без пробелов и разделителей</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f3564-5768">Nine letters or digits with no spaces or delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="f3564-5769">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f3564-5769">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f3564-5770">Девять букв или цифр;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f3564-5770">Nine letters or digits</span></span>
  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="f3564-5771">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f3564-5771">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f3564-5772">Неприменимо</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f3564-5772">Not applicable</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="f3564-5773">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f3564-5773">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f3564-5774">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f3564-5774">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="f3564-5775">Регулярное выражение `Regex_netherlands_eu_passport_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f3564-5775">The regular expression  `Regex_netherlands_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="f3564-5776">Найдено ключевое слово FROM `Keywords_netherlands_eu_passport_number` .</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f3564-5776">A keyword from  `Keywords_netherlands_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
 <!-- EU Passport Number -->
<Entity id="21883626-6245-4f3d-9b61-5cbb43e625ee" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_netherlands_eu_passport_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_netherlands_eu_passport_number" />
        </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="f3564-5777">Keywords</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f3564-5777">Keywords</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f3564-5778">**Keywords_netherlands_eu_passport_number**</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f3564-5778">**Keywords_netherlands_eu_passport_number**</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="f3564-5779">номер паспорта для нидерландского языка</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f3564-5779">dutch passport number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f3564-5780">passport number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f3564-5780">passport number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f3564-5781">номер паспорта Нидерландов</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f3564-5781">netherlands passport number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f3564-5782">недерланден паспурт нуммер</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f3564-5782">nederlanden paspoort nummer</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f3564-5783">паспурт</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f3564-5783">paspoort</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f3564-5784">недерланден паспуртнуммер</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f3564-5784">nederlanden paspoortnummer</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f3564-5785">паспуртнуммер</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f3564-5785">paspoortnummer</span></span>

## <a name="netherlands-tax-identification-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="f3564-5786">Идентификационный номер налога Нидерландов</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f3564-5786">Netherlands tax identification number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="f3564-5787">Этот объект типа конфиденциальной информации доступен только в типе конфиденциальной информации по идентификационному номеру Европейского налога ЕС.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f3564-5787">This sensitive information type entity is only available in the EU Tax Identification Number sensitive information type.</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="f3564-5788">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f3564-5788">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f3564-5789">Девять цифр без пробелов и разделителей</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f3564-5789">Nine digits without spaces or delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="f3564-5790">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f3564-5790">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f3564-5791">Девять цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f3564-5791">Nine digits</span></span> 
  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="f3564-5792">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f3564-5792">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f3564-5793">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f3564-5793">Yes</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="f3564-5794">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f3564-5794">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f3564-5795">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 85 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f3564-5795">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="f3564-5796">Функция `Func_netherlands_eu_tax_file_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f3564-5796">The function  `Func_netherlands_eu_tax_file_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="f3564-5797">Найдено ключевое слово FROM `Keywords_netherlands_eu_tax_file_number` .</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f3564-5797">A keyword from  `Keywords_netherlands_eu_tax_file_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
<span data-ttu-id="f3564-5798">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f3564-5798">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="f3564-5799">Функция `Func_netherlands_eu_tax_file_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f3564-5799">The function  `Func_netherlands_eu_tax_file_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
    
```xml
 <!-- EU Tax File Number -->
<Entity id="e09c07d3-66e5-4783-989d-49ac62748f5f" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_netherlands_eu_tax_file_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_netherlands_eu_tax_file_number" />
        </Pattern>
<Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_netherlands_eu_tax_file_number" />
        </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

## <a name="new-zealand-ministry-of-health-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="f3564-5837">Номер министерства здоровья Новой Зеландии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f3564-5837">New Zealand ministry of health number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="f3564-5838">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f3564-5838">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f3564-5839">Три буквы, пробел (необязательно) и четыре цифры.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f3564-5839">Three letters, a space (optional), and four digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="f3564-5840">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f3564-5840">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f3564-5841">Три буквы (без учета регистра), пробел (необязательно) из четырех цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f3564-5841">Three letters (not case sensitive) a space (optional) four digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="f3564-5842">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f3564-5842">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f3564-5843">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f3564-5843">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="f3564-5844">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f3564-5844">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f3564-5845">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 85 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f3564-5845">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f3564-5846">функция Func_new_zealand_ministry_of_health_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f3564-5846">The function Func_new_zealand_ministry_of_health_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f3564-5847">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_nz_terms;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f3564-5847">A keyword from Keyword_nz_terms is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f3564-5848">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f3564-5848">The checksum passes.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- New Zealand Health Number -->
<Entity id="2b71c1c8-d14e-4430-82dc-fd1ed6bf05c7" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
    <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_new_zealand_ministry_of_health_number" />
        <Any minMatches="1">
          <Match idRef="Keyword_nz_terms" />
        </Any>
    </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

<span data-ttu-id="f3564-5850">Keyword_nz_terms</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f3564-5850">Keyword_nz_terms</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="f3564-5852">Новая Зеландия</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f3564-5852">New Zealand</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="f3564-5853">Здравоохранение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f3564-5853">Health</span></span>

## <a name="norway-identification-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="f3564-5855">Идентификационный номер Норвегии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f3564-5855">Norway identification number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="f3564-5856">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f3564-5856">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f3564-5857">11 цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f3564-5857">11 digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="f3564-5858">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f3564-5858">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f3564-5859">11 цифр:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f3564-5859">11 digits:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f3564-5860">шесть цифр в формате ДДММГГ (дата рождения);</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f3564-5860">Six digits in the format DDMMYY which are the date of birth</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="f3564-5861">индивидуальный номер из трех цифр;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f3564-5861">Three-digit individual number</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="f3564-5862">две проверочные цифры.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f3564-5862">Two check digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="f3564-5863">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f3564-5863">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f3564-5864">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f3564-5864">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="f3564-5865">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f3564-5865">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f3564-5866">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 85 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f3564-5866">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f3564-5867">функция Func_norway_id_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f3564-5867">The function Func_norway_id_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f3564-5868">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_norway_id_number;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f3564-5868">A keyword from Keyword_norway_id_number is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f3564-5869">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f3564-5869">The checksum passes.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f3564-5870">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f3564-5870">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f3564-5871">функция Func_norway_id_numbe находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f3564-5871">The function Func_norway_id_numbe finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f3564-5872">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f3564-5872">The checksum passes.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Norway Identification Number -->
<Entity id="d4c8a798-e9f2-4bd3-9652-500d24080fc3" recommendedConfidence="85" patternsProximity="300">
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
     <IdMatch idRef="Func_norway_id_number"/>
     <Match idRef="Keyword_norway_id_number"/>
  </Pattern>
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
     <IdMatch idRef="Func_norway_id_number"/>
  </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

#### <a name="keyword_norway_id_number"></a><span data-ttu-id="f3564-5874">Keyword_norway_id_number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f3564-5874">Keyword_norway_id_number</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="f3564-5877">ID Number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f3564-5877">ID Number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f3564-5878">Процедура</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f3564-5878">Identification</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f3564-5879">персоннуммер</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f3564-5879">Personnummer</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f3564-5880">фøдселснуммер</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f3564-5880">Fødselsnummer</span></span>

   
## <a name="philippines-unified-multi-purpose-identification-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="f3564-5881">Идентификационный номер единой системы для различных целей Филиппины</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f3564-5881">Philippines unified multi-purpose identification number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="f3564-5882">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f3564-5882">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f3564-5883">12 цифр, разделенных дефисами.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f3564-5883">12 digits separated by hyphens</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="f3564-5884">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f3564-5884">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f3564-5885">12 цифр:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f3564-5885">12 digits:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f3564-5886">четыре цифры;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f3564-5886">Four digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="f3564-5887">дефис;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f3564-5887">A hyphen</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="f3564-5888">семь цифр;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f3564-5888">Seven digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="f3564-5889">дефис;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f3564-5889">A hyphen</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="f3564-5890">одна цифра.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f3564-5890">One digit</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="f3564-5891">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f3564-5891">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f3564-5892">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f3564-5892">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="f3564-5893">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f3564-5893">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f3564-5894">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f3564-5894">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f3564-5895">регулярное выражение Regex_philippines_unified_id находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f3564-5895">The regular expression Regex_philippines_unified_id finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f3564-5896">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_philippines_id.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f3564-5896">A keyword from Keyword_philippines_id is found.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Philippines Unified Multi-Purpose ID number -->
<Entity id="019b39dd-8c25-4765-91a3-d9c6baf3c3b3" recommendedConfidence="75" patternsProximity="300">
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
     <IdMatch idRef="Regex_philippines_unified_id"/>
     <Match idRef="Keyword_philippines_id"/>
  </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="f3564-5897">Keywords</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f3564-5897">Keywords</span></span>
   
#### <a name="keyword_philippines_id"></a><span data-ttu-id="f3564-5898">Keyword_philippines_id</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f3564-5898">Keyword_philippines_id</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="f3564-5899">Unified Multi-Purpose ID</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f3564-5899">Unified Multi-Purpose ID</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="f3564-5900">умид</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f3564-5900">UMID</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="f3564-5901">Identity Card</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f3564-5901">Identity Card</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="f3564-5902">Pinag-isang Multi-Layunin ID</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f3564-5902">Pinag-isang Multi-Layunin ID</span></span>

## <a name="poland-drivers-license-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="f3564-5903">Номер водительского удостоверения для драйвера Польша</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f3564-5903">Poland driver's license number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="f3564-5904">Этот объект типа конфиденциальной информации доступен только в типе конфиденциальной информации номера лицензии для драйвера ЕС.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f3564-5904">This sensitive information type entity is only available in the EU Driver's License Number sensitive information type.</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="f3564-5905">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f3564-5905">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f3564-5906">14 цифр, содержащих 2 косых черты.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f3564-5906">14 digits containing 2 forward slashes</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="f3564-5907">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f3564-5907">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f3564-5908">14 цифр и 2 косых черт:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f3564-5908">14 digits and 2 forward slashes:</span></span>
  
-  <span data-ttu-id="f3564-5909">Пять цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f3564-5909">Five digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="f3564-5910">косая черта;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f3564-5910">A forward slash</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f3564-5911">Две цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f3564-5911">Two digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f3564-5912">косая черта;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f3564-5912">A forward slash</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f3564-5913">семь цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f3564-5913">Seven digits</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="f3564-5914">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f3564-5914">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f3564-5915">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f3564-5915">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="f3564-5916">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f3564-5916">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f3564-5917">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f3564-5917">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="f3564-5918">Регулярное выражение `Regex_poland_eu_driver's_license_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f3564-5918">The regular expression  `Regex_poland_eu_driver's_license_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="f3564-5919">Найдено ключевое слово FROM `Keywords_poland_eu_driver's_license_number` .</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f3564-5919">A keyword from  `Keywords_poland_eu_driver's_license_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
 <!-- EU Driver's License Number -->
<Entity id="b8fe86d1-c056-453b-bfaa-9fe698699ecc" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_poland_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_poland_eu_driver's_license_number" />
        </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="f3564-5920">Keywords</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f3564-5920">Keywords</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f3564-5921">**Keywords_poland_eu_driver "s_license_number**</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f3564-5921">**Keywords_poland_eu_driver's_license_number**</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="f3564-5922">DL #</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f3564-5922">dl#</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f3564-5923">driver license</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f3564-5923">driver license</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f3564-5924">номер водительского удостоверения</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f3564-5924">driver license number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f3564-5925">Лицензия на драйвер</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f3564-5925">driver licence</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f3564-5926">Drivers лик.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f3564-5926">drivers lic.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f3564-5927">drivers license</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f3564-5927">drivers license</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f3564-5928">drivers licence</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f3564-5928">drivers licence</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f3564-5929">driver's license</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f3564-5929">driver's license</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f3564-5930">номер водительского удостоверения</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f3564-5930">driver's license number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f3564-5931">номер лицензии на драйвер</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f3564-5931">driver's licence number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f3564-5932">номер водительского удостоверения</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f3564-5932">driving license number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f3564-5933">длно #</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f3564-5933">dlno#</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f3564-5934">право жазди</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f3564-5934">prawo jazdy</span></span>

## <a name="poland-identity-card"></a><span data-ttu-id="f3564-5935">Идентификационная карточка Польша</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f3564-5935">Poland identity card</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="f3564-5936">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f3564-5936">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f3564-5937">Три буквы и шесть цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f3564-5937">Three letters and six digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="f3564-5938">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f3564-5938">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f3564-5939">Три буквы (без учета регистра), за которыми следуют шесть цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f3564-5939">Three letters (not case sensitive) followed by six digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="f3564-5940">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f3564-5940">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f3564-5941">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f3564-5941">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="f3564-5942">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f3564-5942">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f3564-5943">Политика защиты от потери данных — 75% уверенности, что она обнаружила этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в пределах близости от 300 символов: функция Func_polish_national_id находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f3564-5943">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters: The function Func_polish_national_id finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="f3564-5944">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_polish_national_id_passport_number;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f3564-5944">A keyword from Keyword_polish_national_id_passport_number is found.</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="f3564-5945">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f3564-5945">The checksum passes.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Poland Identity Card-->
<Entity id="25E64989-ED5D-40CA-A939-6C14183BB7BF" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
      <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_polish_national_id" />
          <Match idRef="Keyword_polish_national_id_passport_number" />
      </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

- <span data-ttu-id="f3564-5948">Довóд особисти</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f3564-5948">Dowód osobisty</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f3564-5949">Нумер доводу особистего</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f3564-5949">Numer dowodu osobistego</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f3564-5950">Назва i нумер доводу особистего</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f3564-5950">Nazwa i numer dowodu osobistego</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f3564-5951">Назва i НР доводу особистего</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f3564-5951">Nazwa i nr dowodu osobistego</span></span>

## <a name="poland-national-id-pesel"></a><span data-ttu-id="f3564-5956">Национальный идентификатор (PESEL), Польша</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f3564-5956">Poland National ID (PESEL)</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="f3564-5957">Этот объект типа конфиденциальной информации включен в тип конфиденциальной информации страны ЕС и доступен как отдельный объект типа конфиденциальной информации.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f3564-5957">This sensitive information type entity is included in the EU National Identification Number sensitive information type and is available as a stand alone sensitive information type entity.</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="f3564-5958">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f3564-5958">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f3564-5959">11 цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f3564-5959">11 digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="f3564-5960">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f3564-5960">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f3564-5961">11 последовательных цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f3564-5961">11 consecutive digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="f3564-5962">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f3564-5962">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f3564-5963">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f3564-5963">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="f3564-5964">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f3564-5964">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f3564-5965">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 85 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f3564-5965">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f3564-5966">функция Func_pesel_identification_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f3564-5966">The function Func_pesel_identification_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f3564-5967">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_pesel_identification_number;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f3564-5967">A keyword from Keyword_pesel_identification_number is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f3564-5968">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f3564-5968">The checksum passes.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Poland National ID (PESEL) -->      
<Entity id="E3AAF206-4297-412F-9E06-BA8487E22456" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
      <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_pesel_identification_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keyword_pesel_identification_number" />
      </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

- <span data-ttu-id="f3564-5974">ниеповтарзалнинумер</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f3564-5974">niepowtarzalnynumer</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f3564-5975">НР. PESEL</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f3564-5975">nr.-pesel</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f3564-5976">НР — PESEL</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f3564-5976">nr-pesel</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="f3564-5977">Нумер идентификацижни</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f3564-5977">numer identyfikacyjny</span></span>
